WEBVTT

01:31.030 --> 01:35.030
[Dream of Golden Years]

01:35.900 --> 01:39.140
[2006]

02:08.470 --> 02:09.240
Sorry.

02:10.310 --> 02:11.640
I should've been braver

02:12.360 --> 02:13.680
back then.

02:15.770 --> 02:18.240
[Episode 16 Be Braver]

02:20.960 --> 02:21.960
I meant to tell you

02:22.560 --> 02:23.690
on the very same day.

02:25.150 --> 02:26.880
But when I reached the hospital

02:27.120 --> 02:29.579
and learned that you also
got in an accdient,

02:30.400 --> 02:31.360
I really didn't know

02:31.360 --> 02:32.220
how to tell you.

02:35.710 --> 02:37.240
That day, I had a dream,

02:40.150 --> 02:41.810
where you got injured as well.

02:44.310 --> 02:45.310
But later, you appeared

02:45.310 --> 02:47.040
at the hospital safe and sound.

02:48.240 --> 02:50.240
So I didn't give it too much thought.

02:50.800 --> 02:52.600
I didn't expect Shi Kai would...

02:53.150 --> 02:53.750
That's why

02:55.280 --> 02:57.480
I couldn't bring myself to utter a word.

02:57.590 --> 02:58.450
It was so cruel.

02:59.530 --> 03:00.790
I've even wondered...

03:01.120 --> 03:01.720
if there is

03:02.280 --> 03:03.010
a connection

03:03.150 --> 03:03.840
between

03:04.520 --> 03:05.710
Shi Kai's accident

03:06.590 --> 03:08.250
and the one you and Wei were in.

03:09.430 --> 03:11.030
But I checked multiple times

03:11.470 --> 03:13.330
and confirmed that your car crash

03:13.750 --> 03:15.080
was purely accidental.

03:15.960 --> 03:17.000
Connection?

03:18.190 --> 03:20.800
Perhaps the connection
between these accidents

03:20.800 --> 03:21.860
doesn't lie in you,

03:22.710 --> 03:23.630
but me.

03:24.280 --> 03:25.680
My appearance in this era

03:25.750 --> 03:27.150
is an accident itself.

03:27.680 --> 03:29.520
Will it bring more accidents

03:30.079 --> 03:31.410
to the people around me?

03:31.840 --> 03:32.370
Xiaolan.

03:34.240 --> 03:35.470
After the New Year,

03:36.079 --> 03:37.430
I may have to go back.

03:38.630 --> 03:39.680
Shi Kai's wife wanted

03:39.680 --> 03:40.880
to work in Jingcheng.

03:41.430 --> 03:42.890
I helped her look for a job,

03:43.680 --> 03:45.010
but problems occurred.

03:45.520 --> 03:47.250
She refused to be transferred,

03:47.360 --> 03:48.960
so I have to go back to her aid.

03:49.720 --> 03:50.560
Shi Kai was at work

03:50.560 --> 03:52.420
with me when he had that accident.

03:52.520 --> 03:54.850
I'd like to help his family
as much as I can.

03:55.800 --> 03:57.730
Actually, I've also been thinking

03:58.470 --> 03:59.030
if I am

03:59.030 --> 04:00.630
getting a bit too involved.

04:04.750 --> 04:05.410
Zhou Cheng,

04:06.190 --> 04:08.190
I'm supportive of you helping them,

04:08.360 --> 04:10.080
but there are boundaries.

04:11.030 --> 04:12.160
Think this through:

04:12.960 --> 04:13.870
are you helping

04:14.540 --> 04:15.960
Shi Kai's wife and son because you plan to

04:15.960 --> 04:17.070
take full responsibility

04:17.070 --> 04:18.510
for their future lives,

04:19.560 --> 04:21.290
or because you hope to help them

04:21.510 --> 04:22.710
move on from the pain,

04:23.190 --> 04:24.510
and gradually become independent

04:24.510 --> 04:25.170
and strong?

04:25.190 --> 04:26.240
Of course I hope

04:26.270 --> 04:27.200
they can move on.

04:29.430 --> 04:30.960
Thank you for the reminder.

04:31.600 --> 04:33.000
This time, I'll make sure

04:33.000 --> 04:35.060
the matters are properly dealt with.

04:35.870 --> 04:36.930
Wait for my return.

04:38.750 --> 04:39.390
I will.

05:10.600 --> 05:11.070
Ms. Xia,

05:11.630 --> 05:12.750
I've brought you the car you booked

05:12.750 --> 05:13.560
before the New Year.

05:13.560 --> 05:15.160
What a nice car.

05:15.480 --> 05:17.510
Ms. Xia, you've even bought a car.

05:17.870 --> 05:19.190
I see you're a big shot now.

05:19.190 --> 05:19.650
Come on,

05:20.000 --> 05:21.250
let me take you out for a ride.

05:21.250 --> 05:21.780
Let's go.

05:22.040 --> 05:22.510
Okay.

05:24.920 --> 05:27.120
Here, take a seat in the back, Granny Yu.

05:27.190 --> 05:28.630
Careful. Mind your head.

05:30.240 --> 05:30.570
Okay.

05:31.560 --> 05:32.310
Thank you.

05:32.560 --> 05:33.220
Drive safe.

05:38.090 --> 05:40.350
Everyone gets a red envelope.
Wishing us a fruitful year ahead.

05:40.350 --> 05:41.400
Thanks, Ms. Bai.

05:41.430 --> 05:42.390
I wish you prosperity.

05:42.390 --> 05:44.159
-I wish you prosperity as well.
-Prosperity for everyone.

05:44.159 --> 05:45.360
Sis Bai, where's my red envelope?

05:45.360 --> 05:48.310
Wishing you wealth
and success in all things.

05:48.510 --> 05:49.510
Thanks, Sis Bai.

05:49.510 --> 05:50.430
Here you are.

05:51.720 --> 05:53.650
-Happy New Year!
-Happy New Year!

05:53.680 --> 05:54.540
Happy New Year!

05:54.720 --> 05:55.650
Thanks, Ms. Xia.

05:56.360 --> 05:57.040
Happy New Year, Ms. Xia.

05:57.040 --> 05:58.070
Happy New Year to you too.

05:58.070 --> 05:58.750
Let it be a fantastic year.

05:58.750 --> 05:59.120
Thank you.

05:59.120 --> 05:59.600
Happy New Year.

05:59.600 --> 06:00.070
Thanks, Ms. Xia.

06:00.070 --> 06:01.720
Wishing us all a productive year.

06:01.720 --> 06:02.270
Happy New Year.

06:02.270 --> 06:02.600
Thank you.

06:02.600 --> 06:03.360
Happy New Year.

06:03.360 --> 06:03.950
Thanks, Ms. Xia.

06:03.950 --> 06:05.160
Happy New Year.
Let there be a great start.

06:05.160 --> 06:05.970
Is Chen in there?

06:05.970 --> 06:07.000
Yes, Mr. Chen is in his office.

06:07.000 --> 06:07.400
Got it.

06:10.000 --> 06:10.480
Chen,

06:10.680 --> 06:11.410
Happy New...

06:12.000 --> 06:12.860
Happy New Year.

06:13.510 --> 06:15.040
What happened to your face?

06:15.800 --> 06:16.830
N-N-Nothing.

06:17.310 --> 06:18.710
How is it nothing? You...

06:19.070 --> 06:20.470
I just didn't sleep well.

06:21.600 --> 06:22.390
Is something wrong at home...

06:22.390 --> 06:23.190
Chen Xiliang!

06:24.680 --> 06:25.480
Chen Xiliang?

06:26.630 --> 06:27.360
It's my wife.

06:33.680 --> 06:34.190
Honey.

06:36.070 --> 06:37.120
You have no shame,

06:37.120 --> 06:37.800
Chen Xiliang.

06:37.800 --> 06:38.480
I knew

06:38.600 --> 06:39.310
you wouldn't suddenly

06:39.310 --> 06:40.950
open a factory in Shengcheng.

06:40.950 --> 06:41.720
Are you going to give

06:41.720 --> 06:43.070
all the money to this temptress?

06:43.070 --> 06:43.830
We'll talk at home.

06:43.830 --> 06:44.480
Stop yelling here.

06:44.480 --> 06:45.680
Listen, she's my business partner.

06:45.680 --> 06:46.480
Business partner?

06:46.480 --> 06:47.310
What business partner?

06:47.310 --> 06:48.520
I bet she's your sexual partner!

06:48.520 --> 06:49.600
You're a piece of filth!

06:49.600 --> 06:50.630
Are you sleeping with...

06:50.630 --> 06:51.190
Stop it.

06:51.240 --> 06:51.870
Chen Xiliang.

06:51.870 --> 06:52.430
Stop with this fuss!

06:52.430 --> 06:53.720
Explain the whole thing to your wife.

06:53.720 --> 06:54.650
I'm leaving now.

06:54.680 --> 06:55.360
Let go of me!

06:55.800 --> 06:56.750
Tell me what you've done!

06:56.750 --> 06:58.210
Enough. Get out of the way.

06:58.360 --> 06:58.830
This

06:58.830 --> 07:00.890
shameless woman seduced my husband!

07:01.120 --> 07:02.270
They are having an affair!

07:02.270 --> 07:03.310
Stop yelling here!

07:03.310 --> 07:04.160
How many times have I told you?

07:04.160 --> 07:05.310
She's a shareholder of my company.

07:05.310 --> 07:06.430
Stop being unreasonable.

07:06.430 --> 07:07.070
I'm telling you,

07:07.070 --> 07:07.630
at this rate,

07:07.630 --> 07:08.720
the trust between us will be gone,

07:08.720 --> 07:09.920
and I'll divorce you!

07:12.430 --> 07:13.230
Chen Xiliang,

07:13.920 --> 07:14.510
divorce her or not—

07:14.510 --> 07:15.630
it has nothing to do with me.

07:15.630 --> 07:16.720
Get your family affairs

07:16.720 --> 07:17.380
sorted out.

07:17.560 --> 07:18.510
I'll withdraw my investment!

07:18.510 --> 07:19.040
Move!

07:19.510 --> 07:20.570
I'm sorry. This...

07:21.000 --> 07:21.800
You must stay!

07:22.160 --> 07:23.070
How dare you leave?

07:23.070 --> 07:23.720
Come back here!

07:23.720 --> 07:24.480
This is enough.

07:24.480 --> 07:24.800
Stop yelling!

07:24.800 --> 07:26.600
You have no conscience, Chen Xiliang!

07:26.600 --> 07:27.000
You...

07:27.360 --> 07:28.360
Enough is enough!

07:28.360 --> 07:29.040
Are you done with the fuss?

07:29.040 --> 07:29.430
No!

07:29.510 --> 07:30.310
If Luna fails,

07:30.430 --> 07:31.430
I'll go bankrupt.

07:31.680 --> 07:33.680
Let's see who you can ask for money then.

07:33.680 --> 07:35.040
No more talking. Let's go.

07:35.040 --> 07:35.750
We'll get a divorce

07:35.750 --> 07:37.000
in the Civil Affairs Bureau!

07:37.000 --> 07:37.600
Divorce?

07:37.870 --> 07:39.000
A divorce it is then!

07:39.000 --> 07:40.120
I'm telling you, Chen Xiliang,

07:40.120 --> 07:40.720
if you divorce me,

07:40.720 --> 07:42.120
I won't let you take a single dime away!

07:42.120 --> 07:43.040
I won't take even a dime!

07:43.040 --> 07:44.190
You can keep all the money at home.

07:44.190 --> 07:45.650
All I want is my brand Luna!

07:49.600 --> 07:52.560
[Clothing Tycoon Brutally Killed by
His Treacherous Young Wife]

07:51.630 --> 07:52.040
Wait.

07:52.920 --> 07:55.159
Chen Xiliang's treacherous second wife

07:55.159 --> 07:56.490
used to be his mistress.

07:56.950 --> 07:57.870
Could it be...

07:58.600 --> 07:59.630
that I've become

07:59.630 --> 08:01.030
Chen Xiliang's mistress

08:01.870 --> 08:03.120
in this world?

08:04.130 --> 08:05.360
This is ridiculous.

08:10.920 --> 08:12.240
We're not able to establish

08:12.240 --> 08:13.360
a materials center yet.

08:13.360 --> 08:14.800
For now, let's stay grounded

08:14.800 --> 08:16.190
and focus on our small shop.

08:16.190 --> 08:17.070
Wei and I have

08:17.070 --> 08:18.160
learned our lesson.

08:18.160 --> 08:20.190
We won't overestimate ourselves again.

08:20.190 --> 08:21.650
Xiaolan, don't you worry.

08:22.190 --> 08:23.600
Kang Wei is really down-to-earth now.

08:23.600 --> 08:24.660
I won't be worried.

08:27.830 --> 08:28.430
Xiaolan,

08:28.600 --> 08:30.070
Cheng will be back next week.

08:30.070 --> 08:31.000
Just be patient.

08:33.720 --> 08:34.179
Coming!

08:36.750 --> 08:37.480
You're here.

08:38.320 --> 08:39.360
Hurry, come on in.

08:40.690 --> 08:41.419
I've told you

08:41.440 --> 08:42.750
not to bring anything over,

08:42.750 --> 08:44.080
since this is your home.

08:44.630 --> 08:45.090
Come on.

08:45.320 --> 08:46.030
Take a seat.

08:46.240 --> 08:46.720
Wei.

08:48.150 --> 08:49.350
I own this apartment,

08:49.750 --> 08:50.880
but it's not my home.

08:52.670 --> 08:53.870
Actually, I came here

08:54.480 --> 08:55.740
to tell you something.

09:04.240 --> 09:05.240
I need some more time

09:05.240 --> 09:06.700
to consider what you said.

09:20.840 --> 09:21.550
Guo.

09:21.630 --> 09:22.230
Granny Yu.

09:22.600 --> 09:23.910
Any mails for me?

09:24.030 --> 09:25.150
Or a package?

09:25.390 --> 09:25.990
Granny Yu,

09:26.160 --> 09:26.910
there hasn't been a mail

09:26.910 --> 09:29.110
or a package for you
during the New Year.

09:30.000 --> 09:31.320
Could they have been missed?

09:31.320 --> 09:32.850
Check carefully, will you?

09:32.910 --> 09:34.670
Granny Yu, we've checked several times.

09:34.670 --> 09:35.670
Nothing could've been missed.

09:35.670 --> 09:36.390
If there were anything for you,

09:36.390 --> 09:38.790
we would've delivered it
to your house already.

09:38.790 --> 09:40.030
I'm leaving then, Granny Yu.

09:40.030 --> 09:41.490
Please let me get through.

09:41.630 --> 09:42.390
Thanks.

09:42.410 --> 09:43.070
No problem.

09:57.240 --> 09:57.840
Xiaolan.

09:58.870 --> 09:59.480
Xiaolan?

10:00.960 --> 10:02.750
You seem distracted. How come?

10:04.440 --> 10:06.300
Are you fighting with Zhou Cheng?

10:07.440 --> 10:09.240
I'm not fighting with Zhou Cheng,

10:09.240 --> 10:10.670
but myself.

10:11.840 --> 10:13.440
So many accidents have happened recently.

10:13.440 --> 10:14.770
I can't help but suspect

10:15.080 --> 10:16.610
if my appearance in this era

10:16.630 --> 10:18.890
has changed the fates of those around me.

10:19.030 --> 10:20.120
No.

10:20.390 --> 10:22.450
I'm not fighting with him, Granny Yu.

10:25.150 --> 10:25.870
Granny Yu,

10:26.630 --> 10:28.030
you've seen many things.

10:28.150 --> 10:29.150
I have a question.

10:29.680 --> 10:31.120
Do you think a person's fate

10:31.120 --> 10:32.180
is predetermined?

10:33.630 --> 10:35.000
Young people like you

10:35.200 --> 10:37.030
always think about stuff

10:37.390 --> 10:39.080
like fate and destiny.

10:40.360 --> 10:42.000
Dear, none of that means anything.

10:42.000 --> 10:43.480
The thought of it is futile.

10:43.480 --> 10:45.840
Living every day to its fullest

10:46.150 --> 10:47.750
matters more than anything.

10:49.600 --> 10:50.960
Aren't you worried that your decisions

10:50.960 --> 10:52.890
might change someone else's fate?

10:53.080 --> 10:54.680
Do you have no regrets at all?

10:55.120 --> 10:55.750
What if you had

10:55.750 --> 10:58.350
refused to go to Nanyang
with others years ago?

11:01.690 --> 11:03.820
Sorry. I shouldn't have brought it up.

11:06.030 --> 11:07.690
It's fine. That's not a taboo.

11:08.730 --> 11:10.190
I've thought about it too.

11:11.790 --> 11:12.670
If...

11:13.480 --> 11:15.480
I could do it all over again,

11:16.510 --> 11:17.270
I'm not sure

11:17.270 --> 11:18.910
what decision I would make.

11:19.910 --> 11:22.000
Suppose I made the same decision,

11:22.440 --> 11:24.120
it wouldn't necessarily lead to

11:24.120 --> 11:25.390
the same result.

11:26.240 --> 11:26.970
Everyone...

11:27.580 --> 11:29.670
is pushed forward by time.

11:30.720 --> 11:31.720
Living a life

11:32.080 --> 11:33.480
is like dreaming a dream.

11:34.120 --> 11:35.780
Don't be too full of yourself.

11:36.030 --> 11:37.870
Does anyone really have the power

11:37.870 --> 11:39.600
to change someone else's fate?

11:53.610 --> 11:55.120
[Divorce Certificate]

11:57.320 --> 11:57.720
Xia,

11:59.150 --> 12:00.750
I've sorted everything out.

12:00.750 --> 12:01.720
I left all the cash at home

12:01.720 --> 12:02.720
with Lin Meijuan.

12:03.240 --> 12:04.720
Now, Luna is all I have.

12:05.270 --> 12:07.400
Can you not withdraw your investment?

12:09.630 --> 12:10.290
This is bad.

12:11.000 --> 12:12.510
I have really become Chen's "mistress"

12:12.510 --> 12:13.970
in the original timeline.

12:14.630 --> 12:15.360
However,

12:15.670 --> 12:17.120
if I were her,

12:17.390 --> 12:19.450
there's no way I'd harm Chen Xiliang.

12:19.720 --> 12:21.030
So, in this timeline,

12:21.030 --> 12:22.030
Chen Xiliang will

12:22.080 --> 12:24.080
still become the future clothing tycoon.

12:24.080 --> 12:25.120
But he might not

12:25.120 --> 12:26.250
end up being killed.

12:26.840 --> 12:27.970
Granny Yu was right.

12:28.270 --> 12:29.870
Perhaps I'm just too full of myself.

12:29.870 --> 12:31.120
There is a chance

12:31.600 --> 12:32.470
that the recent happenings

12:32.470 --> 12:34.330
weren't caused by my appearance.

12:35.270 --> 12:35.720
Xia,

12:36.750 --> 12:38.010
please say something.

12:38.270 --> 12:39.270
Are you still mad?

12:39.480 --> 12:40.630
How can I not?

12:41.000 --> 12:41.600
I told you to sort out

12:41.600 --> 12:43.120
things between you and your wife.

12:43.120 --> 12:44.320
Is this how you did it?

12:45.630 --> 12:47.840
A husband and wife may not
always be on the same boat

12:47.840 --> 12:48.970
or strive together,

12:49.360 --> 12:51.790
but they shouldn't hold each other back
at least.

12:51.790 --> 12:52.390
Chen,

12:52.840 --> 12:54.970
I think you were right to get a divorce.

13:00.390 --> 13:02.080
Have all the assets been divided?

13:02.080 --> 13:03.440
I'd hate for Luna to be dragged

13:03.440 --> 13:04.240
into some sort

13:04.240 --> 13:06.100
of divorce dispute in the future.

13:06.550 --> 13:07.550
It's all settled.

13:07.630 --> 13:08.160
I just...

13:09.390 --> 13:10.720
Does this mean you won't

13:11.000 --> 13:12.530
withdraw your investment?

13:14.030 --> 13:15.690
I'll take your silence as yes.

13:17.550 --> 13:18.750
Chen Xiliang,

13:18.870 --> 13:20.440
how come I never noticed before

13:20.440 --> 13:21.770
that you're so cunning?

13:22.240 --> 13:24.110
You've even got Granny Yu on your side.

13:24.110 --> 13:25.550
It's not like I used devious means.

13:25.550 --> 13:26.240
I just...

13:26.240 --> 13:27.720
had to do what I had to do.

13:33.440 --> 13:34.570
My phone's ringing.

13:36.870 --> 13:37.270
Hello?

13:37.900 --> 13:38.630
Mr. Cui.

13:40.240 --> 13:42.570
The issue
for the second half of the month?

13:43.220 --> 13:44.150
No problem.

13:44.150 --> 13:44.630
Okay.

13:44.910 --> 13:45.550
Thanks.

13:46.120 --> 13:47.200
Thank you so much.

13:47.390 --> 13:47.790
Bye.

13:49.360 --> 13:51.080
You were just whining to me
about being poor.

13:51.080 --> 13:52.360
But now you're using
a brick phone already.

13:52.360 --> 13:53.360
Stop teasing me.

13:53.550 --> 13:54.080
I just...

13:54.550 --> 13:57.080
need it to b-bring in projects.
Can't you see?

13:57.630 --> 13:58.670
Honestly, there isn't

13:58.670 --> 14:00.270
much money left in my pocket.

14:00.480 --> 14:01.200
Besides,

14:01.280 --> 14:02.760
Luna is a mid-range brand.

14:02.790 --> 14:04.650
We have to boost its image, right?

14:04.670 --> 14:06.320
That call was from Mr. Cui.

14:06.600 --> 14:08.320
He said Wu Kaili's photos
from the Chinese New Year Gala

14:08.320 --> 14:11.050
could get on
the second half of the month's issue.

14:11.600 --> 14:13.400
About what you told me last time,

14:13.670 --> 14:15.800
t-that "native advertising" thingy,

14:16.070 --> 14:17.400
how do we approach that?

14:19.120 --> 14:20.150
Native advertising

14:20.150 --> 14:22.720
means hiding advertisements

14:22.720 --> 14:24.580
in seemingly ordinary articles.

14:24.750 --> 14:26.720
For instance, we can write a piece

14:27.240 --> 14:28.360
in an editor's tone,

14:28.360 --> 14:29.200
saying that one day,

14:29.200 --> 14:30.440
he or she went across a shop

14:30.440 --> 14:31.720
and discovered the items for sale

14:31.720 --> 14:33.850
were from a domestic brand named Luna.

14:33.870 --> 14:35.600
He or she then took a look inside

14:36.100 --> 14:37.440
and found that Luna was the brand

14:37.440 --> 14:39.870
that Wu Kaili wore to
the Chinese New Year Gala.

14:39.870 --> 14:40.790
Readers nowadays

14:40.790 --> 14:42.200
haven't gotten very alert

14:42.200 --> 14:43.280
about such content,

14:43.280 --> 14:44.360
so they could easily be tricked

14:44.360 --> 14:45.550
by cunning businessmen like you

14:45.550 --> 14:46.680
without knowing it.

14:46.720 --> 14:48.780
H-How am I a cunning businessman now?

14:49.440 --> 14:50.550
But this idea of yours

14:50.550 --> 14:51.270
is brilliant.

14:51.270 --> 14:53.000
I would never come up with that.

14:53.320 --> 14:54.720
In the era I'm from,

14:54.960 --> 14:56.030
this is common practice.

14:56.030 --> 14:56.630
Tell me more

14:56.630 --> 14:57.160
about it.

14:57.200 --> 14:57.790
You just gave

14:57.790 --> 14:58.840
a few lines. Tell me more

14:58.840 --> 14:59.320
of that stuff.

14:59.320 --> 15:00.520
I-I'll write it down.

15:02.470 --> 15:04.380
[Fashion Guide]

15:05.080 --> 15:05.880
Okay. Thanks.

15:08.510 --> 15:10.080
Clothes by Luna?

15:10.270 --> 15:11.720
Even that Gangdao celebrity Wu Kaili

15:11.720 --> 15:12.630
wears this brand.

15:12.630 --> 15:13.480
So beautiful!

15:13.630 --> 15:14.690
I love this outfit.

15:14.870 --> 15:15.360
Look,

15:15.750 --> 15:16.630
clothes by Luna.

15:16.510 --> 15:21.820
[Luna]

15:23.320 --> 15:24.510
Look, that's Wu Kaili!

15:24.510 --> 15:25.670
Yeah. She's so pretty.

15:25.110 --> 15:26.390
[The same brand wore by Gangdao celebrity
Wu Kaili in the Chinese New Year Gala]

15:41.840 --> 15:43.080
Class act by Mr. Cui.

15:43.600 --> 15:44.480
Next, we'll be racing

15:44.480 --> 15:45.360
against time.

15:45.840 --> 15:46.750
After this issue hits the stands,

15:46.750 --> 15:48.550
there will be about a ten-day buzz.

15:48.550 --> 15:49.270
We must open the store

15:49.270 --> 15:50.800
within this period of time.

15:51.200 --> 15:52.860
What should be the exact date?

15:55.320 --> 15:56.180
February 20th,

15:56.440 --> 15:57.700
the Lantern Festival.

15:58.000 --> 15:58.730
Good choice.

16:03.510 --> 16:03.910
Hello?

16:04.270 --> 16:04.910
Cheng.

16:05.750 --> 16:07.480
Are you done with your business yet?

16:07.480 --> 16:08.600
The Luna store is going to open.

16:08.600 --> 16:09.550
You have to be back soon,

16:09.550 --> 16:10.630
or you'll miss the opening.

16:10.630 --> 16:12.670
What kind of supportive boyfriend are you?

16:12.670 --> 16:13.510
Cut it out.

16:14.440 --> 16:15.510
I'm almost done here.

16:15.510 --> 16:16.640
I'll be back in time.

16:17.150 --> 16:17.750
Well...

16:18.550 --> 16:19.750
How has Xiaolan been?

16:20.150 --> 16:22.010
You're asking me how she's doing?

16:22.910 --> 16:24.240
Aren't you two in touch?

16:25.390 --> 16:26.440
I've tried calling

16:26.440 --> 16:27.500
Granny Yu's place.

16:27.750 --> 16:29.350
Yet Xiaolan is never around.

16:29.840 --> 16:31.550
Xiaolan is just too busy

16:31.670 --> 16:32.670
to talk to you.

16:33.360 --> 16:33.890
Alright.

16:34.730 --> 16:35.720
Anyway, if anything comes up,

16:35.720 --> 16:36.550
try helping out

16:36.550 --> 16:37.410
more actively.

16:38.200 --> 16:39.060
I'm hanging up.

16:44.440 --> 16:44.970
Xiaolan,

16:45.910 --> 16:47.640
are you really just being busy?

16:56.390 --> 16:56.910
This

16:57.200 --> 16:59.400
is Ms. Xia, who I told you about earlier.

16:59.750 --> 17:00.680
In the next week,

17:00.840 --> 17:01.870
you'll receive

17:02.030 --> 17:03.690
pre-job training right here.

17:03.790 --> 17:05.000
So that's Ms. Xia?

17:05.440 --> 17:06.920
She looks even younger than me.

17:06.920 --> 17:07.790
Watch your tongue.

17:07.790 --> 17:08.990
Observe discipline.

17:09.940 --> 17:10.829
Hello, everyone.

17:10.829 --> 17:11.960
I am Xia Xiaolan,

17:12.310 --> 17:14.160
also a co-owner of Luna.

17:14.510 --> 17:15.480
Luna is positioned

17:15.480 --> 17:16.550
as mid-range women's wear.

17:16.550 --> 17:18.240
We strive for a competitive edge
in service,

17:18.240 --> 17:19.700
style, and brand effects.

17:19.750 --> 17:20.750
Your image exactly

17:20.750 --> 17:22.480
represents the brand's image.

17:23.000 --> 17:25.349
You will be trained in areas
of etiquette, styling,

17:25.349 --> 17:26.430
sales scripts,

17:26.589 --> 17:28.119
and marketing strategies.

17:29.200 --> 17:29.960
Now, please

17:30.270 --> 17:31.130
meet Granny Yu,

17:31.550 --> 17:33.150
your etiquette instructor.

17:35.400 --> 17:35.930
Alright.

17:36.750 --> 17:39.070
I'd like to lay some ground rules now.

17:39.480 --> 17:41.400
Training involves hardships.

17:42.200 --> 17:44.060
Have all of you had breakfast yet?

17:44.590 --> 17:45.310
-Yes.
-Yes.

17:46.270 --> 17:46.680
Good.

17:48.070 --> 17:50.830
Now, please stand against the wall.

17:53.750 --> 17:54.810
Did you not hear me?

17:55.400 --> 17:56.030
Go!

17:56.280 --> 17:56.690
Hurry.

17:56.720 --> 17:57.850
Class has begun. Go!

18:03.440 --> 18:05.440
Pretty looks are wasted

18:05.750 --> 18:07.830
without an upright posture,

18:08.160 --> 18:10.420
for elegance is what gives them meaning.

18:10.960 --> 18:11.790
Stand against the wall.

18:11.790 --> 18:13.590
Shoulders against the wall too.

18:13.590 --> 18:14.650
Your heels as well.

18:14.750 --> 18:16.720
Every part mentioned must touch the wall.

18:16.720 --> 18:17.790
Straighten your back.

18:17.790 --> 18:19.050
Today's class is about

18:19.200 --> 18:20.800
how to put on a perfect smile.

18:21.000 --> 18:22.530
Everyone can smile, right?

18:22.750 --> 18:23.510
The point is,

18:23.720 --> 18:24.960
how to smile cutely

18:25.240 --> 18:26.550
and beautifully.

18:27.070 --> 18:28.200
Seeing such lovely smiles,

18:28.200 --> 18:29.060
customers will

18:29.240 --> 18:30.920
feel welcome when they get in the store

18:30.920 --> 18:33.110
and have the desire to buy our clothes.

18:33.510 --> 18:34.550
So, today,

18:34.680 --> 18:36.340
you'll practice how to smile.

18:39.590 --> 18:42.160
I'm having you walk in place
with books on your heads

18:42.160 --> 18:44.960
so you can learn
how to keep your posture straight.

18:45.680 --> 18:46.940
Lift your legs higher.

18:47.720 --> 18:48.790
Goodbye, Granny Yu.

18:48.790 --> 18:49.270
Bye.

18:52.650 --> 18:53.310
These 7 points

18:53.310 --> 18:54.720
conclude

18:54.720 --> 18:56.510
the clothing sales skills

18:56.510 --> 18:57.510
I just mentioned.

18:57.590 --> 18:58.920
What makes a good outfit

18:59.110 --> 19:00.200
is the styling.

19:00.440 --> 19:01.770
Now, let's give it a try.

19:02.240 --> 19:03.840
You Li, please come forward.

19:03.930 --> 19:05.920
Remember the way she looks and feels

19:05.920 --> 19:06.880
in this dress.

19:07.000 --> 19:08.730
Twenty-two, twenty-three...

19:10.880 --> 19:11.480
Very good.

19:12.880 --> 19:13.480
Very good.

19:15.110 --> 19:15.570
Come on.

19:17.270 --> 19:17.750
So pretty.

19:17.750 --> 19:19.750
This is the charm of styling.

19:21.350 --> 19:22.680
Granny Yu, here we come.

19:22.680 --> 19:23.940
Granny Yu, we're here.

19:41.550 --> 19:43.750
Greetings, Ms. Xia, Ms. Liu.

19:43.830 --> 19:46.070
Welcome to Luna Womenswear.

19:48.830 --> 19:50.160
How wonderful.

19:50.480 --> 19:52.270
Granny Yu, you are amazing.

19:52.720 --> 19:53.680
How did you train them

19:53.680 --> 19:54.830
to be so professional?

19:54.830 --> 19:55.760
Perfect, right?

19:57.600 --> 19:58.720
Before the opening,

19:58.720 --> 19:59.790
there is an extra assignment

19:59.790 --> 20:00.750
for you all.

20:01.160 --> 20:02.480
Shengcheng is a port city

20:02.480 --> 20:03.620
adjacent to Gangdao.

20:03.620 --> 20:04.650
Many of our customers

20:04.650 --> 20:06.160
will be from overseas

20:06.180 --> 20:06.980
or Gangdao.

20:07.440 --> 20:08.880
So, in your spare time,

20:08.880 --> 20:10.400
try learning Cantonese

20:10.400 --> 20:11.200
and English.

20:11.440 --> 20:12.790
After all, one more language you speak

20:12.790 --> 20:14.760
means one more potential customer.

20:14.760 --> 20:15.440
You know that

20:15.440 --> 20:17.300
without me explaining it, right?

20:17.310 --> 20:18.240
Now, I announce,

20:18.310 --> 20:19.440
you've all successfully

20:19.440 --> 20:20.840
completed the training!

20:25.000 --> 20:25.960
I wish you

20:26.160 --> 20:28.720
a grand opening and a booming business!

20:32.430 --> 20:33.000
Bye.

20:33.030 --> 20:34.690
-Bye.
-You girls are the best!

20:35.000 --> 20:36.200
Get home safe.

20:36.550 --> 20:36.960
Sure!

20:36.960 --> 20:37.790
Don't be late tomorrow.

20:37.790 --> 20:38.240
Okay.

20:38.750 --> 20:39.750
Good work.

20:44.550 --> 20:46.480
It's been a long time since he left.

20:46.510 --> 20:48.370
Aren't you going to do something?

20:48.400 --> 20:50.200
Zhou Cheng told me he'd solve the problem.

20:50.200 --> 20:50.880
I trust him.

20:53.030 --> 20:54.490
Trust is all that matters.

20:56.920 --> 20:57.450
Let's go.

20:58.110 --> 20:59.040
Ms. Xia, Ms. Xia!

20:59.400 --> 21:00.200
Wait a moment.

21:00.550 --> 21:01.510
What is it, You?

21:02.200 --> 21:02.790
Ms. Xia,

21:03.000 --> 21:03.790
I was too embarrassed to say this

21:03.790 --> 21:05.350
with that many people around just now.

21:05.350 --> 21:06.810
I'd love to learn English.

21:06.930 --> 21:07.790
But I have no idea

21:07.790 --> 21:09.110
where to start,

21:09.550 --> 21:11.880
since I dropped out from middle school...

21:12.440 --> 21:13.240
That's okay.

21:13.730 --> 21:15.560
If you're completely new at it,

21:15.590 --> 21:17.120
just start with listening.

21:17.350 --> 21:18.920
Forget about reading and writing.

21:18.920 --> 21:20.550
First, try to memorize the sentences

21:20.550 --> 21:21.510
and phrases

21:21.510 --> 21:23.530
that are often used in life or at work.

21:23.530 --> 21:24.640
Tell you what, come with me.

21:24.640 --> 21:25.970
I'll get you some books.

21:26.440 --> 21:27.350
Thank you, Ms. Xia.

21:27.350 --> 21:27.750
Here.

21:28.270 --> 21:29.590
Tomorrow, both stores in Shengcheng

21:29.590 --> 21:31.160
and Longcheng will open at the same time.

21:31.160 --> 21:33.110
I'm sure everything will go smoothly.

21:33.110 --> 21:33.790
Chen,

21:33.960 --> 21:35.160
don't be too nervous.

21:35.160 --> 21:36.560
Get a good night's sleep.

21:36.830 --> 21:38.630
May the openings be successful.

21:46.030 --> 21:46.690
Zhou Cheng,

21:47.550 --> 21:48.640
I've sorted out

21:48.640 --> 21:49.680
my feelings.

21:51.000 --> 21:52.860
Have you solved your problem yet?

21:54.000 --> 21:55.000
I miss you so much.

22:01.970 --> 22:07.930
♪ Watching the flowers fall,
lonely I ask the night sky ♪

22:08.590 --> 22:13.810
♪ Is spring hazy where you are? ♪

22:15.660 --> 22:20.470
♪ Time is upside down,
the seasons intertwine ♪

22:21.210 --> 22:27.320
♪ Fate seems to want us to stay silent ♪

22:28.770 --> 22:31.720
♪ Time is so stingy ♪

22:31.740 --> 22:35.080
♪ It takes away even the memories ♪

22:35.980 --> 22:38.580
♪ But I still remember ♪

22:38.770 --> 22:43.060
♪ The promises of love ♪

22:43.260 --> 22:45.720
♪ Call out to me with all your strength ♪

22:45.740 --> 22:50.450
♪ Let the whole starry sky sparkle ♪

22:49.880 --> 22:50.410
Xiaolan.

22:50.470 --> 22:53.040
♪ Respond to me with all your heart ♪

22:52.000 --> 22:53.030
This has been

22:53.060 --> 22:57.610
♪ Across the ends of the earth,
we won't stop ♪

22:54.110 --> 22:55.170
a really long week.

22:58.090 --> 23:01.860
♪ No matter how fierce the storms,
I won't back down ♪

23:01.880 --> 23:06.080
♪ I'll run toward the harbor
where you are ♪

23:02.030 --> 23:02.890
I have properly

23:03.110 --> 23:04.240
handled the matter.

23:06.310 --> 23:07.070
Previously,

23:06.990 --> 23:11.560
♪ Together, forever ♪

23:07.920 --> 23:09.000
I didn't realize

23:09.590 --> 23:10.400
Shi Kai's family

23:10.400 --> 23:11.730
didn't need pity or help

23:12.350 --> 23:13.680
beyond all boundaries.

23:14.720 --> 23:16.650
They should stand on their own feet

23:16.920 --> 23:18.050
and face the future.

23:19.160 --> 23:20.360
I should also stand up

23:21.440 --> 23:22.640
and go on with my life—

23:28.920 --> 23:30.180
a life shared with you.

23:36.430 --> 23:39.550
[Passbook for Current Deposits]

23:40.160 --> 23:41.270
It contains the money

23:41.270 --> 23:42.110
I earned from the business

23:42.110 --> 23:43.510
I did with Wei in the past,

23:43.790 --> 23:45.790
along with my salary for over a year,

23:46.030 --> 23:46.590
bonuses,

23:47.400 --> 23:48.510
and even the lucky money I received

23:48.510 --> 23:49.310
in childhood.

23:49.680 --> 23:50.310
Anyway,

23:50.720 --> 23:51.920
every penny to my name

23:52.440 --> 23:53.500
is in this account.

23:54.510 --> 23:56.000
I'd love for you to have it all.

23:56.000 --> 23:57.110
What are you doing?

23:57.720 --> 23:59.880
Throwing money at me instead of making

24:00.400 --> 24:01.530
romantic gestures?

24:04.110 --> 24:05.440
I know you don't care for
my little savings,

24:05.440 --> 24:06.900
now that you're a big boss.

24:08.590 --> 24:10.350
You're pretty rich, counselor.

24:10.350 --> 24:11.550
There's over 60,000.

24:12.000 --> 24:12.790
Alright then.

24:12.790 --> 24:14.240
I'll keep it safe for you.

24:17.440 --> 24:18.100
Zhou Cheng.

24:19.830 --> 24:21.240
Actually, I also owe you

24:21.240 --> 24:21.900
an apology.

24:23.210 --> 24:25.520
These days, with Luna stores' openings

24:25.550 --> 24:26.920
and many other affairs,

24:27.200 --> 24:28.270
I became so busy

24:28.590 --> 24:29.790
that I neglected you.

24:31.240 --> 24:33.270
To show how sorry I am,

24:33.720 --> 24:34.830
should I also hand over

24:34.830 --> 24:36.090
my passbook to you too?

24:38.510 --> 24:39.640
I wouldn't dare take

24:39.640 --> 24:41.170
such huge advantage of you.

24:41.920 --> 24:42.450
Xiaolan.

24:44.310 --> 24:45.000
I know...

24:46.200 --> 24:47.000
you've been through

24:47.000 --> 24:47.830
a lot lately.

24:49.790 --> 24:51.850
I should've spent more time with you.

24:52.400 --> 24:53.060
I assure you

24:53.680 --> 24:54.550
that from now on,

24:54.550 --> 24:55.510
I'll definitely be

24:55.510 --> 24:57.170
a more supportive boyfriend.

24:57.720 --> 24:58.780
When you're tired,

24:59.240 --> 25:00.700
just lean on my shoulders.

25:02.350 --> 25:03.680
I'm very tired now.

25:04.510 --> 25:06.510
Then lean on my shoulders, will you?

25:26.110 --> 25:28.630
[Warm Congratulations on
the Grand Opening of Luna Clothing Store]

26:10.750 --> 26:11.160
Bravo!

26:11.400 --> 26:12.590
Bravo!

26:14.240 --> 26:15.590
Luna Clothing Store...

26:16.000 --> 26:18.440
is officially open!

26:21.700 --> 26:23.640
For our grand opening,
12% is off on all items!

26:23.640 --> 26:25.450
Please come in and have a look!

26:25.480 --> 26:25.880
Bravo!

26:25.880 --> 26:27.000
Welcome!

26:28.830 --> 26:30.680
Welcome! Welcome!

26:30.700 --> 26:32.300
Watch your step. Be careful.

26:32.310 --> 26:32.920
Welcome!

26:32.960 --> 26:33.620
Be careful.

26:38.110 --> 26:39.200
Here's the checkout counter.

26:39.200 --> 26:40.730
Everything is discounted.

26:41.000 --> 26:41.460
Please,

26:41.550 --> 26:42.110
this way.

26:42.240 --> 26:42.680
Hello.

26:43.070 --> 26:43.720
Follow me.

26:43.720 --> 26:44.270
Let's go!

26:44.550 --> 26:45.080
Let's go.

26:46.070 --> 26:46.590
Here!

26:47.510 --> 26:48.240
Here, here.

26:49.440 --> 26:49.920
Sis Bai,

26:50.400 --> 26:51.200
foreign customers, huh?

26:51.200 --> 26:51.930
I saw them.

26:52.320 --> 26:53.440
The lights are really

26:53.440 --> 26:54.640
making a difference.

26:54.640 --> 26:55.680
-Yes.
-Everything looks high-class.

26:55.680 --> 26:56.640
How prosperous.

26:58.040 --> 26:59.280
This is my first time

26:59.310 --> 27:00.640
seeing Auntie at work.

27:00.880 --> 27:02.480
Quite different from usual.

27:02.680 --> 27:03.550
When Auntie

27:03.550 --> 27:04.550
was in Jingcheng,

27:04.570 --> 27:06.770
she could already manage a store alone.

27:11.160 --> 27:12.960
What are you looking at? Go help.

27:12.960 --> 27:13.920
What can I help with?

27:13.920 --> 27:15.380
Every staffer is busy now.

27:16.920 --> 27:17.720
This is yours.

27:19.400 --> 27:20.250
-Welcome.
-Welcome.

27:20.250 --> 27:20.750
Come on in, please.

27:20.750 --> 27:22.640
A 12% discount on everything
for today's grand opening.

27:22.640 --> 27:23.700
Take a look inside.

27:23.720 --> 27:25.120
Welcome! Please come in!

27:34.640 --> 27:35.830
Mr. Du wishes Luna—

27:36.240 --> 27:39.030
a successful opening
and a booming business!

27:42.350 --> 27:43.550
What kind of stunt

27:43.840 --> 27:45.300
is Du Zhaohui pulling now?

27:45.640 --> 27:49.000
The flowers have arrived.
Why are these people still around?

27:49.000 --> 27:50.400
Fellas, thank you.

27:50.720 --> 27:51.790
Tell Mr. Du I say thank you

27:51.790 --> 27:52.640
when you get back.

27:52.640 --> 27:53.840
The flowers can stay.

27:53.920 --> 27:54.920
You may leave now.

27:55.000 --> 27:55.830
Got it, Ms. Xia.

27:55.830 --> 27:57.110
Thank you, Ms. Xia!

28:04.160 --> 28:04.760
Everyone,

28:05.350 --> 28:06.880
we're having something light today—

28:06.880 --> 28:08.790
goji berry soup with assorted mushroom.

28:08.790 --> 28:10.120
Come on, help yourself.

28:11.510 --> 28:13.710
I had this soup simmered for a long time.

28:14.030 --> 28:14.830
Young Master,

28:15.180 --> 28:16.450
the task in Shengcheng

28:16.920 --> 28:18.960
is complete. Flowers were sent,

28:19.120 --> 28:20.110
and everything else taken care of.

28:20.110 --> 28:22.750
The ribbon-cutting ceremony
is in the afternoon.

28:22.750 --> 28:23.720
I hate this stupid

28:23.720 --> 28:25.050
Spring Reception Party

28:25.350 --> 28:27.810
for holding me back
from the ribbon cutting.

28:27.920 --> 28:29.200
If only I could cut the ribbon

28:29.200 --> 28:30.330
with Xia Xiaolan...

28:33.440 --> 28:35.300
Young Master, care for some soup?

28:41.830 --> 28:43.490
A toast from Zhaoji to you all.

28:44.400 --> 28:46.260
Many thanks, uncles and aunties.

28:47.880 --> 28:49.410
Do look after my son, folks.

28:51.960 --> 28:53.270
I'm not eating anything. Go get the car.

28:53.270 --> 28:53.680
Yes.

28:57.830 --> 28:59.310
Alright. Be seated, please.

28:59.310 --> 28:59.640
Come.

29:01.310 --> 29:01.640
Hey!

29:01.830 --> 29:02.440
Everyone,

29:02.640 --> 29:03.960
enjoy the feast.

29:06.030 --> 29:06.830
Young Master!

29:10.440 --> 29:11.830
Have the Shengcheng police
taken action yet?

29:11.830 --> 29:13.070
Yes, they have.

29:13.830 --> 29:14.960
I hope my old man will like

29:14.960 --> 29:15.920
this spring celebration gift

29:15.920 --> 29:16.510
from me.

29:16.750 --> 29:17.610
He surely will.

29:17.750 --> 29:18.750
Xia Xiaolan has always wanted

29:18.750 --> 29:19.790
to see me do serious business, right?

29:19.790 --> 29:20.200
Right.

29:21.030 --> 29:22.310
I'll show her how I get it done this time.

29:22.310 --> 29:23.200
No problem.

29:23.350 --> 29:24.160
Let's go back to Shengcheng.

29:24.160 --> 29:24.510
Sure!

29:29.590 --> 29:30.390
Young Master,

29:30.440 --> 29:31.640
it's "Lady Plastic."

29:44.790 --> 29:46.880
Why stare at us? Plastic freak.

29:48.000 --> 29:48.790
Young Master,

29:48.790 --> 29:50.240
when we get to Shengcheng,

29:50.240 --> 29:50.920
shall we head straight

29:50.920 --> 29:52.400
to Ms. Xia's clothing store?

29:52.400 --> 29:54.270
Forget it. Let's go back to the hotel.

29:54.270 --> 29:55.310
Send a message to Ms. Xia.

29:55.310 --> 29:55.880
Tell her

29:56.270 --> 29:57.470
that I, Du Zhaohui, am

29:57.510 --> 29:58.920
going to do serious business.

29:58.920 --> 29:59.580
Sure thing.

30:00.550 --> 30:02.080
Impressive, Young Master.

30:08.310 --> 30:09.510
Take your time trying them on.

30:09.510 --> 30:10.840
There are many options.

30:11.030 --> 30:12.630
This color is also very good.

30:16.230 --> 30:17.890
Do you have another shoe size?

30:18.350 --> 30:18.880
This?

30:19.240 --> 30:20.310
Yes, this is cool.

30:20.970 --> 30:23.690
[Luna]

30:28.710 --> 30:33.000
[Closed]

30:58.890 --> 31:02.530
[Spring, 1990] [Panpan the Panda;
Embracing the Asian Games]

31:03.340 --> 31:04.890
[Closed]

31:09.000 --> 31:09.350
Four.

31:10.240 --> 31:13.640
Six, seven, eight, nine, ten, eleven,

31:13.830 --> 31:14.430
twelve...

31:14.720 --> 31:15.510
Ms. Xia, Ms. Liu,

31:15.510 --> 31:16.030
we've restocked

31:16.030 --> 31:17.000
the sold-out items.

31:17.000 --> 31:18.350
This is today's inventory list.

31:18.350 --> 31:19.240
Okay. Back to your work then.

31:19.240 --> 31:19.590
Yes.

31:24.640 --> 31:25.000
Mom,

31:25.680 --> 31:27.070
we can open branch stores now.

31:27.070 --> 31:27.640
Really?

31:32.690 --> 31:33.440
Being on the Chinese New Year Gala

31:33.440 --> 31:34.750
and in magazines
has really brought great publicity

31:34.750 --> 31:35.550
to our brand.

31:35.880 --> 31:37.240
The initial investments were huge.

31:37.240 --> 31:38.830
I can't believe we've made profits

31:38.830 --> 31:40.030
within just one year.

31:40.270 --> 31:41.480
Though the costs on factories,

31:41.480 --> 31:42.440
channels, and stores

31:42.440 --> 31:43.880
in the early stages were massive,

31:43.880 --> 31:45.690
at least we didn't have to pay
any middlemen.

31:45.690 --> 31:46.720
We'll benefit from this mode

31:46.720 --> 31:47.580
in the long run,

31:47.750 --> 31:49.280
as it not only reduces costs

31:49.440 --> 31:52.050
but also enables us
to control the brand's quality.

31:52.050 --> 31:53.830
Before this year's summer collection

31:53.830 --> 31:54.510
is launched,

31:54.510 --> 31:56.160
we can open two branch stores.

31:56.160 --> 31:57.160
The managers for them

31:57.160 --> 31:59.200
will be selected from current staff.

31:59.200 --> 32:00.330
Just keep an eye out.

32:00.640 --> 32:00.970
Okay.

32:01.200 --> 32:02.400
I share the same view.

32:02.720 --> 32:05.650
Where do you think
we should place the branch stores?

32:05.920 --> 32:07.200
Shengcheng and Longcheng.

32:07.200 --> 32:08.310
One store in each city.

32:08.310 --> 32:09.110
The new ones will have the same

32:09.110 --> 32:10.480
specifications as the existing ones.

32:10.480 --> 32:11.610
Exactly identical.

32:11.920 --> 32:13.480
Before the summer collection is out,

32:13.480 --> 32:14.960
they'll be open for business, right?

32:14.960 --> 32:15.560
By the way,

32:15.590 --> 32:17.270
how's the summer collection coming along?

32:17.270 --> 32:18.070
Wait a second.

32:24.440 --> 32:25.170
Here you are.

32:25.640 --> 32:26.900
One more catalog here.

32:34.960 --> 32:36.290
The designs are not bad.

32:36.440 --> 32:37.240
But I think

32:37.240 --> 32:38.400
we can add in

32:38.400 --> 32:39.640
some sporty elements

32:39.920 --> 32:41.380
to go with the Asian Games.

32:41.510 --> 32:41.910
Got it.

32:43.310 --> 32:43.720
Also,

32:44.000 --> 32:45.240
design a series

32:45.310 --> 32:47.200
of special outfits

32:47.510 --> 32:50.030
and make them a limited edition
for the Asian Games.

32:50.030 --> 32:51.310
The mighty spirit of Asia, right?

32:51.310 --> 32:52.310
Limited edition?

32:53.270 --> 32:54.000
What is that?

32:54.640 --> 32:56.100
By that, I mean we will only

32:57.310 --> 32:58.440
sell 10,000 pieces.

32:59.800 --> 33:02.060
Xia, you're really full of clever ideas.

33:07.400 --> 33:08.460
It's finally done.

33:08.720 --> 33:10.000
In fact,
the renovation of the two dinning halls

33:10.000 --> 33:11.110
was finished long ago.

33:11.110 --> 33:12.110
But we had to wait
till they were inspected

33:12.110 --> 33:13.640
together with the larger corporates' works

33:13.640 --> 33:15.040
to get the final payment.

33:15.350 --> 33:16.160
You know what, Xiaolan?

33:16.160 --> 33:17.200
In the recent two months,

33:17.200 --> 33:18.270
calls have been flooding in

33:18.270 --> 33:19.680
from customers requiring

33:19.680 --> 33:21.540
Yuanhui's renovation services.

33:22.070 --> 33:23.680
Yuanhui has really made a name

33:23.680 --> 33:25.140
for itself in Shengcheng.

33:25.680 --> 33:26.880
With steady business

33:26.920 --> 33:28.780
and the franchise fees from Luna,

33:28.960 --> 33:30.720
we can start building a materials center!

33:30.720 --> 33:32.240
This place looks great to me.

33:32.240 --> 33:33.640
According to Xiaolan, we should choose

33:33.640 --> 33:35.200
a location with relevant distribution hubs

33:35.200 --> 33:36.480
in the vicinity.

33:36.750 --> 33:38.030
I've noticed
that Uncle Yong kept going to this place

33:38.030 --> 33:39.030
when he did renovation projects.

33:39.030 --> 33:41.200
There should be relevant shops around.

33:41.200 --> 33:42.350
I also think it's a good place.

33:42.350 --> 33:43.000
There are

33:43.000 --> 33:44.460
wide roads front and back,

33:44.550 --> 33:45.720
making it convenient for our big trucks

33:45.720 --> 33:47.120
to load and unload stuff.

33:47.200 --> 33:48.590
Yes, and most importantly,

33:48.590 --> 33:49.550
it provides a broad enough space

33:49.550 --> 33:50.800
for us to not only display products,

33:50.800 --> 33:51.580
but also store items,

33:51.580 --> 33:52.640
leading to high efficiency.

33:52.640 --> 33:53.510
Given that we are

33:53.510 --> 33:54.440
not suppliers,

33:54.440 --> 33:55.090
but distributors,

33:55.090 --> 33:56.050
we have to attract customers

33:56.050 --> 33:57.680
by offering good service and convenience.

33:57.680 --> 33:58.210
Xiaolan,

33:58.240 --> 33:59.240
what do you think?

34:00.030 --> 34:00.960
What do I think?

34:02.130 --> 34:03.610
I think you have really...

34:03.640 --> 34:04.680
hit your stride

34:04.680 --> 34:06.010
in doing business, Wei.

34:06.310 --> 34:07.110
You bet I have.

34:07.110 --> 34:07.510
I'm telling you,

34:07.510 --> 34:08.920
my brain here is now filled

34:08.920 --> 34:10.980
with wisdom and talent.

34:12.800 --> 34:14.060
There's one more thing

34:14.550 --> 34:16.010
I need to discuss with you.

34:17.030 --> 34:19.110
That is, I'd like to invite my uncle
to be a shareholder

34:19.110 --> 34:20.510
of the materials center.

34:21.150 --> 34:23.210
For one thing, this is a large project

34:23.280 --> 34:24.550
involving massive capital.

34:24.550 --> 34:25.110
One more helper

34:25.110 --> 34:26.310
means more strength.

34:26.710 --> 34:27.840
For another thing,

34:27.920 --> 34:30.000
my uncle is a renovation constractor.

34:30.000 --> 34:30.880
Sometimes he lands

34:30.880 --> 34:32.139
major deals on his own.

34:32.280 --> 34:33.070
If he becomes a shareholder,

34:33.070 --> 34:34.400
those deals will be ours as well.

34:34.400 --> 34:35.480
It'll be more convenient.

34:35.480 --> 34:36.480
What do you think?

34:36.800 --> 34:37.550
I agree with it.

34:37.550 --> 34:38.760
I would've brought that idea up

34:38.760 --> 34:39.820
if Xiaolan hadn't.

34:39.909 --> 34:40.790
Look, now,

34:40.909 --> 34:42.370
Sis Bai handles supplies,

34:42.510 --> 34:44.110
Xiaolan is charge of the big picture

34:44.110 --> 34:44.800
and marketing,

34:44.800 --> 34:45.510
and Uncle Yong

34:45.510 --> 34:46.800
brings in big orders.

34:47.120 --> 34:47.710
But look at me.

34:47.710 --> 34:48.710
All I can offer is a little money

34:48.710 --> 34:50.040
and no other resources.

34:50.510 --> 34:51.800
If Uncle Yong doesn't become

34:51.800 --> 34:52.710
a shareholder, I will be

34:52.710 --> 34:54.360
too embarrassed to take up a spot.

34:54.360 --> 34:55.560
I also agree with you.

34:56.000 --> 34:56.360
Good.

34:57.240 --> 34:58.000
Oh right, Xiaolan,

34:58.000 --> 34:59.070
have you come up with a name

34:59.070 --> 35:00.530
for the materials center?

35:01.320 --> 35:03.380
Say it if you already have one in mind.

35:03.880 --> 35:05.110
I did think of a name.

35:05.440 --> 35:07.000
The center can be called

35:07.190 --> 35:08.960
"Happy Home Materials."

35:09.190 --> 35:10.190
What do you think?

35:11.030 --> 35:11.800
Pretty good.

35:12.360 --> 35:13.820
It feels less commercial,

35:14.000 --> 35:15.060
and more personal.

35:15.400 --> 35:16.460
Let's go with that.

35:18.030 --> 35:18.490
Senior.

35:20.280 --> 35:22.480
I just came back from the police station.

35:22.480 --> 35:24.170
That case about neighborhood disputes

35:24.170 --> 35:24.670
was finally closed.

35:24.670 --> 35:25.500
Okay, I got it.

35:38.190 --> 35:38.710
Senior,

35:39.840 --> 35:40.670
any progress

35:41.110 --> 35:42.570
on the construction site?

35:47.840 --> 35:48.710
In this day and age,

35:48.710 --> 35:49.920
finding a hidden temp worker

35:49.920 --> 35:52.000
is like looking for a needle
in a haystack.

35:52.000 --> 35:53.190
Everyone who has made

35:53.190 --> 35:55.150
such a big mistake at work like he did

35:55.150 --> 35:57.010
would likely get scared and hide.

35:57.550 --> 35:58.880
Shi Kai was a good fella.

35:59.920 --> 36:01.780
It's a shame he had that accident.

36:03.280 --> 36:04.510
It was not an accident.

36:04.510 --> 36:05.170
Zhou Cheng.

36:12.360 --> 36:13.360
Here is a case

36:13.360 --> 36:14.800
about a trading company in Shengcheng.

36:14.800 --> 36:16.860
It's complex and somewhat connected

36:17.190 --> 36:17.990
to Hangcheng.

36:18.320 --> 36:19.440
Handling it will probably take

36:19.440 --> 36:21.480
tremendous time and effort from you.

36:21.480 --> 36:22.920
But once you nail it,

36:23.280 --> 36:24.590
that will be a great step up

36:24.590 --> 36:26.190
for both you and the law firm.

36:26.880 --> 36:28.280
Take a look at it quickly.

36:28.710 --> 36:29.960
Your girlfriend is running
a prosperous business.

36:29.960 --> 36:30.800
You shouldn't fall behind,

36:30.800 --> 36:31.280
right?

36:33.030 --> 36:34.000
It's a new year.

36:34.910 --> 36:35.570
Zhou Cheng,

36:37.440 --> 36:38.840
you need to look forward.

36:49.400 --> 36:50.510
-Cheers!
-Cheers!

36:54.550 --> 36:56.440
Hotpot in the cold.

36:56.800 --> 36:58.800
Seafood in the heat.

36:59.190 --> 37:01.230
A joy nothing can beat.

37:01.230 --> 37:03.400
Then what's to eat
when it's neither cold nor hot?

37:03.400 --> 37:04.480
I'm not telling you.

37:04.480 --> 37:05.010
Oh right.

37:05.360 --> 37:05.880
I heard news

37:05.880 --> 37:07.210
about Du Zhaohui today.

37:10.360 --> 37:11.220
What happened?

37:11.400 --> 37:12.660
I'm being serious now.

37:13.550 --> 37:14.450
Do you remember

37:14.760 --> 37:16.150
the massive crackdown on vice

37:16.150 --> 37:17.550
in Shengcheng last year?

37:18.190 --> 37:19.480
Today, in the police station,

37:19.480 --> 37:21.200
I heard that the whole thing was caused

37:21.200 --> 37:22.080
by Du Zhaohui.

37:22.110 --> 37:23.510
He reported the dance halls his family ran
for involvement

37:23.510 --> 37:25.040
in illegal sexual service.

37:25.710 --> 37:26.510
So that was

37:26.510 --> 37:28.150
the serious business he set his mind to.

37:28.150 --> 37:30.070
He can't do business in Shengcheng

37:30.070 --> 37:32.400
without committing an act of allegiance.

37:32.400 --> 37:33.670
Therefore, he reported

37:33.670 --> 37:34.930
such illicit business

37:35.120 --> 37:36.960
to prove that he is pure in thought,

37:36.960 --> 37:38.290
and upright in conduct.

37:38.630 --> 37:39.190
I wonder

37:39.190 --> 37:40.400
if he put on this show

37:40.420 --> 37:42.350
for the government or for Xiaolan.

37:46.110 --> 37:47.440
Are you stuffed or what?

37:47.800 --> 37:48.710
I'm stuffed.

37:48.710 --> 37:49.510
I was just joking.

37:49.510 --> 37:50.370
Check, please!

37:51.070 --> 37:52.800
Hello, bring me the check please!

37:52.800 --> 37:53.280
Sir!

37:53.400 --> 37:55.280
Qiang, get the check for this table.

37:55.280 --> 37:56.400
Come carry the items!

37:56.400 --> 37:57.160
Coming!

38:01.630 --> 38:02.550
You...

38:04.030 --> 38:04.480
You...

38:04.480 --> 38:05.010
It's you,

38:05.320 --> 38:07.110
the man who fixed my arm!

38:08.440 --> 38:09.280
I remember now.

38:09.280 --> 38:10.150
He's that thief!

38:10.150 --> 38:11.190
He's not the thief.

38:11.190 --> 38:12.920
No, I mean, he caught the thief.

38:13.710 --> 38:14.770
All of you are here?

38:15.370 --> 38:16.150
Good to see you.

38:16.150 --> 38:17.400
Has your arm recovered?

38:17.400 --> 38:18.070
Yes.

38:18.110 --> 38:19.280
It's been a long time, right?

38:19.280 --> 38:20.840
Didn't expect to run into you here.

38:20.840 --> 38:22.700
None of you will pay for this meal.

38:22.760 --> 38:23.360
It's on me.

38:23.630 --> 38:24.090
Well...

38:24.280 --> 38:25.510
Is this your restaurant?

38:25.510 --> 38:26.920
Yes, as a matter of fact, it is.

38:26.920 --> 38:28.110
That's Qiang, a good friend of mine.

38:26.970 --> 38:31.470
♪ I'm never tired by your side
during this long journey ♪

38:28.190 --> 38:29.850
He also owns this restaurant.

38:31.110 --> 38:32.510
I used to be a seaman.

38:31.780 --> 38:36.970
♪ We walk through
every leg of it together ♪

38:32.800 --> 38:33.230
Now,

38:33.320 --> 38:34.400
I'm done drifting around.

38:34.400 --> 38:35.880
That's why I'm running this restaurant
with my friend.

38:35.880 --> 38:37.000
Do come often, guys.

38:37.000 --> 38:37.800
There are many special offers.

38:37.500 --> 38:39.570
♪ As I climb over a peak ♪

38:38.360 --> 38:38.710
Thanks.

38:38.710 --> 38:39.600
-Thanks.
-Thanks.

38:39.600 --> 38:42.170
♪ Another peak appears before my eyes ♪

38:39.710 --> 38:41.280
What should we call you?

38:42.590 --> 38:43.480
My name is Pan Baohua.

38:42.660 --> 38:44.190
♪ Keep the goals high ♪

38:44.070 --> 38:45.070
People usually call me San.

38:44.220 --> 38:47.420
♪ Let your ideals always lead the way ♪

38:46.440 --> 38:47.480
Nice to meet you, San.

38:47.480 --> 38:48.290
My name is Bai Zhenzhu.

38:48.290 --> 38:50.280
♪ Moments of joy and sorrow ♪

38:49.670 --> 38:50.110
White

38:50.300 --> 38:52.990
♪ Swirl around us ♪

38:52.500 --> 38:53.830
You're from Bai Martial Arts School,
right?

38:53.400 --> 38:56.430
♪ Admiring snow in the wind
and flowers in the fog ♪

38:54.630 --> 38:55.190
Right.

38:55.800 --> 38:57.070
You've heard of Bai Martial Arts School?

38:56.460 --> 38:58.460
♪ Let's spin with joy ♪

38:57.510 --> 38:58.280
Yes, as it is known to

38:58.280 --> 38:59.480
everyone who practices martial arts.

38:58.480 --> 39:00.210
♪ Don't hinge on petty things ♪

38:59.920 --> 39:00.920
You've practiced martial arts?

39:00.230 --> 39:01.610
♪ Savor the happiness ♪

39:01.360 --> 39:02.230
We must have

39:01.640 --> 39:03.640
♪ Around you every day ♪

39:02.360 --> 39:03.660
a friendly fight one day.

39:03.660 --> 39:05.520
♪ I hope you still believe ♪

39:03.710 --> 39:04.440
Definitely.

39:05.000 --> 39:05.960
Nice to make your acquaintance today.

39:05.600 --> 39:09.420
♪ Beautiful scenes and happy times
are not far away ♪

39:06.190 --> 39:07.070
This meal is on me.

39:07.070 --> 39:08.150
Do come more often, guys.

39:08.150 --> 39:09.070
Sure. Thanks.

39:09.070 --> 39:09.580
Thanks.

39:09.440 --> 39:11.630
♪ I'll use laughter ♪

39:09.710 --> 39:10.710
We're leaving then.

39:10.710 --> 39:11.240
Let's go.

39:11.650 --> 39:14.330
♪ To bury all the pain ♪

39:11.760 --> 39:12.290
Let's go.

39:13.030 --> 39:13.590
Take care.

39:13.590 --> 39:14.150
Don't leave anything behind.

39:14.150 --> 39:14.510
See you later.

39:14.350 --> 39:17.030
♪ I don't care for the raindrops ♪

39:16.000 --> 39:16.530
Take care

39:17.050 --> 39:19.620
♪ As I'm determined to march forward ♪

39:18.150 --> 39:19.590
The clams tasted really good.

39:19.590 --> 39:20.190
Good, huh?

39:20.800 --> 39:22.000
Qiang, pack a portion of clams to go!

39:22.000 --> 39:22.630
Sis Bai,

39:23.080 --> 39:24.290
not full yet, are you?

39:24.320 --> 39:25.150
I-I am full.

39:25.230 --> 39:26.230
We'll come again.

39:27.040 --> 39:27.600
Bye!

39:27.630 --> 39:28.840
Okay. Take care.

39:32.650 --> 39:33.760
I heard the business

39:33.760 --> 39:35.710
of Xiaolan's store is booming, isn't it?

39:35.710 --> 39:36.360
Yes, it is.

39:36.710 --> 39:38.280
I'm told there will be branch stores.

39:38.280 --> 39:39.190
Really?

39:40.840 --> 39:41.280
Mom.

39:42.440 --> 39:43.700
You're back, Xiaolan.

39:44.150 --> 39:45.480
I heard from your mother

39:46.030 --> 39:48.030
that you're opening branch stores.

39:48.960 --> 39:49.490
Yes, I am.

39:50.400 --> 39:51.800
So there will be new staff

39:52.030 --> 39:53.690
and training sessions again?

39:54.590 --> 39:56.850
I've really invited trouble, haven't I?

39:57.710 --> 39:58.550
I want to quit.

39:59.440 --> 40:01.360
But we're out of options.

40:01.760 --> 40:03.420
No one but you is up to the task.

40:04.710 --> 40:05.550
Granny Yu,

40:05.800 --> 40:06.670
you'll be in charge

40:06.670 --> 40:08.000
of training Luna staff

40:08.030 --> 40:09.590
in the future.

40:10.030 --> 40:11.030
After all, there will be

40:11.030 --> 40:12.360
more and more Luna stores.

40:12.360 --> 40:13.550
Each and every staffer

40:13.550 --> 40:15.040
at Luna franchises

40:15.070 --> 40:17.070
will have to be trained by you first.

40:18.370 --> 40:19.930
How many franchise stores

40:19.960 --> 40:21.020
do you plan to open?

40:21.440 --> 40:22.500
This many in a year.

40:22.800 --> 40:23.530
Five stores?

40:24.920 --> 40:25.920
Fifty stores.

40:26.480 --> 40:27.210
There will be

40:27.510 --> 40:28.710
500 stores in 3 years.

40:29.480 --> 40:30.760
Have you gone crazy?

40:31.440 --> 40:32.200
Sorry.

40:32.230 --> 40:34.230
This old lady won't play along.

40:34.710 --> 40:36.450
Granny Yu...

40:36.480 --> 40:37.480
Given the workload,

40:37.480 --> 40:39.190
you must be straightforward

40:39.440 --> 40:40.370
and name a price.

40:40.590 --> 40:42.190
I'm a capitalist now.

40:42.920 --> 40:44.800
Then I'll name a sky-high price.

40:45.110 --> 40:46.170
Sure. Just name it.

40:47.110 --> 40:48.110
I'll mull it over.

40:48.320 --> 40:48.960
Okay.

40:48.980 --> 40:50.190
Think carefully about it.

40:50.190 --> 40:51.920
Look at this lassie and granny.

40:54.590 --> 40:55.550
Please wait a moment.

40:55.550 --> 40:57.810
The store will be open for business soon.

40:58.510 --> 40:59.910
Hello, Ms. Xia, Mr. Chen.

41:00.280 --> 41:00.970
Sorry.

41:01.000 --> 41:02.400
The store will open soon.

41:03.890 --> 41:04.590
You're here, Xiaolan.

41:04.590 --> 41:04.960
Mom.

41:05.630 --> 41:06.150
Mr. Chen, Ms. Xia.

41:06.150 --> 41:06.680
Mrs. Liu.

41:06.710 --> 41:07.240
Mr. Chen.

41:08.110 --> 41:09.070
Before the store is open,

41:09.070 --> 41:10.550
there's already a long queue outside.

41:10.550 --> 41:12.760
They're all here for
the Asian Games limited edition clothing.

41:12.760 --> 41:13.220
Ms. Xia.

41:13.400 --> 41:13.930
Mr. Chen.

41:14.280 --> 41:15.360
Only ten pieces are avaible

41:15.360 --> 41:16.690
in each store every day.

41:16.760 --> 41:18.760
They sell out within 5 minutes
after opening.

41:18.760 --> 41:20.090
Should we provide more?

41:20.280 --> 41:20.800
No.

41:21.400 --> 41:23.400
Limited edition clothing
is a hunger marketing strategy.

41:23.400 --> 41:24.550
If everyone can buy it,

41:24.550 --> 41:25.920
the tactic won't work anymore.

41:25.920 --> 41:26.510
Besides,

41:26.840 --> 41:28.230
when the limited edition clothing
sells out,

41:28.230 --> 41:30.290
we can offer similar items, can't we?

41:34.150 --> 41:35.920
That shop across the street
has been leased?

41:35.920 --> 41:36.800
Just a few days ago,

41:36.800 --> 41:38.110
there was still a "For Rent" sign.

41:38.110 --> 41:39.570
It has been rented out now.

41:39.800 --> 41:41.730
I'm not sure what it sells, though.

42:06.960 --> 42:08.030
Please come again.

42:13.670 --> 42:14.400
Hello, Wang.

42:14.480 --> 42:15.010
Mrs. Liu,

42:15.320 --> 42:16.380
shall we leave now?

42:16.590 --> 42:16.980
Sure.

42:17.190 --> 42:18.360
Wait till I get changed.

42:18.360 --> 42:18.760
Okay.

42:24.710 --> 42:25.190
Wang.

42:26.280 --> 42:26.800
Ms. Xia,

42:27.230 --> 42:28.030
you're here too.

42:28.030 --> 42:29.150
Where are you

42:29.150 --> 42:29.800
taking my mother?
